    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cards and Guns 是一款自上而下视角的竞技场射击 Roguelite 游戏。你需要击败一波又一波的怪物。选择多样化的卡牌和升级来打造独特的构筑，努力生存到最后。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >默认自动射击武器，并提供手动瞄准选项</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三种游戏模式：经典、生存者和无尽</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁全新卡牌、角色和强化道具</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集材料，在商店购买卡牌和升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无尽的可重玩性</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界排行榜</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无障碍选项</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >三种游戏模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>经典模式： </strong>在每波持续 20 到 100 秒的怪物攻击中生存下来，尽可能在时间内消灭更多怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329160/extras/33e3a70040d48c0841bffc958acc0f1d.avif?t=1728637025\" width=610 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存者模式： </strong>面对成百上千只怪物组成的无情部落，努力生存 40 分钟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329160/extras/abb81e9dcab36cf3e09b4d2f5754327a.avif?t=1728637025\" width=610 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无尽模式： </strong>面对成百上千只怪物组成的无情部落，尽可能生存下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329160/extras/ffd44f650486fe6399a9afc5aec5ab49.avif?t=1728637025\" width=610 height=210 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态构筑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样化的角色、卡牌和升级供你选择，每次游玩都会带来全新的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329160/extras/97f3614c63fe6d56918268c75cb1b999.avif?t=1728637025\" width=610 height=210 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无尽的可重玩性</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cards and Guns 提供了无尽的可重玩性！测试你的技能，创造更高的分数！</p>",
